descriptionHtml:
After much tinkering with my character's face model I am finally satisfied with how she looks (pretty good I think)

Mods I am using;

Better Makeup for SKSE- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?

True Brows- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50307/?

True Eyes- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49963/?

ApachiiSkyHair- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35092/?

UNP BLESSED BODY- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37900/?

Armour Mods;

Northgirl Armour- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/38053/?

Sexy Transparent Zipsuit(for the heels)- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50301/?

Elisyum Clothing UNPB- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71439/?

I take no credit for the meshes I am simply uploading my face preset for RaceMenu. All textures an meshes are the right of their respective owners.

To install the preset you will requite SKSE and RaceMenu they can be found here;

http://skse.silverlock.org/

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?

[u]
[/u][b][u]INSTALLATION:[/u]
[/b]
After downloading the preset file navigate to your skyrim data folder, most likely under Steam\steamapps\Skyrim\Data
navigate to the SKSE folder, Plugins, CharGen, Presets, and place the file in there. 

Start up Skyrim open the console using the `~ key and type "showracemenu" goto the presets tab in the top right and hit F9 to load presets,
select the file that you dropped into the presets folder earlier and you should be good to go.


If you would like to use the face preset in any of your Mod screenshots or Youtube videos ext, please give me some credit for it via a link to this page, it took me around 10 hours to get her looking this mighty fine. So, yeah. 

ENJOY, cheers Dae.
